    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.9-10_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">9</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="caps">F.P.M.</hi></addrLine>
                        <addrLine>345 Hope St</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>PRovidence,</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Rhode Island</addrLine>
                    </address>
                
                    <dateline>
                        345 Hope
                        January 21, 1958
                    </dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Darlings,</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>As ususal no words equal to expressing my devotion and gratitude for Dr. Neihardt's last letter. Couldn't count the times I've read it &#8212; couldn't say how much it means. The reading brought forth spontaneous little laughs of delight and pleasure in you. That's <hi rend="underline">news</hi> these days if I laugh. (Had to lay aside my little jokes for awhile) Imagine you sent "it" _ <hi rend="underline"><hi rend="caps">AIR</hi> Mail Special Del.</hi></p>
                
                <p>Now &#8212; because of you, Dr. <hi rend="caps">N</hi>, <unclear/>, Dr. <hi rend="caps">B</hi>&#8212; I've been <hi rend="underline">recommended</hi> <unclear>at</unclear> Brown &#8212; will register &#8212; will start &#8212; &amp; will write again. Thank you with all my <unclear>heart</unclear>.</p> <closer><salute>Love</salute>, <signed>Pat.</signed></closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.9-10_0002"/>
                
                <ab type="return">
                    <hi rend="caps">F.P.M.</hi>
                    345 Hope St.
                    Providence
                    <hi rend="caps">R.I.</hi>
                </ab>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">10</fw>
                
                <note>AiR <hi rend="triple underline">MAiL</hi></note>
                
                <note><hi rend="underline">AiR MaiL</hi></note>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    PROVIDENCE
                    JAN 21
                    830 PM
                    1958
                    R.I.
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>3 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>U.S. POSTAGE 3¢
                        IN GOD WE TRUST
                        LIBERTY</p>
                </figure>                
                <figure>
